data.description: Welcome to this well maintained 3 bdr 2.25 bath home on a 1/3 of an acre lot. The main floor features a living room with vaulted ceilings, a kitchen, and a dining room. The lower level has a large family room with a fireplace, a laundry room and a half bath. The upper floor has a primary bedroom with a walk-in closet & 3/4 bath, 2 additional bedrooms, and a full bath. The large corner lot has apple, plum, and pear trees, flowers and shrubs. The back yard is fenced with a raised garden bed. There is a 2 car garage and plenty of parking. There are solar panels that provide a ton of savings on your energy bill. Don't miss the community's park with private access to Long Lake. Close to schools, shopping entertainment, I5 and JBLM.
